    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering a broad torque curve and 320 hp. The longitudinal drivetrain is paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, offering precise gear synchronization and mechanical feel. Key reliability enhancements include an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced water pump and low-temp thermostat. The suspension retains its factory-intended kinematics with updated Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the multi-link rear geometry tracks true under lateral load. The braking system remains sharp with four-piston monobloc calipers and ventilated rotors. This is a mechanically robust specimen optimized for the enthusiast who values chassis feedback and powertrain integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
